  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Analyzing the Request**\n\nI\'m currently dissecting the user\'s request. It seems they want a landing page for \"D-CURE Plus,\" an herbal medication. Crucially, they\'ve provided a full landing page image as a reference, which I\'m now studying to understand their specific design and content expectations. This will be my primary guide.\n\n\n**Inspecting the Visuals**\n\nI\'m now deep-diving into the visual details gleaned from the image and the user\'s explicit instructions. The user desires an app mirroring a specific landing page layout. I\'ve noted crucial elements like the navbar with logo, links (\"\340\246\271\340\247\213\340\246\256\", \"\340\246\211\340\246\252\340\246\225\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\340\246\244\340\246\276\", \"\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\241\340\246\277\340\246\223\", \"\340\246\260\340\246\277\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\211\"), and a deep green \"\340\246\205\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\201\340\246\250\" button. Also, I have been making note of a hero section with a badge, title, and description. I will now gather metadata, including the green color, and all fonts.\n\n\n**Extracting Essential Data**\n\nI\'ve moved on to gathering key data. I\'ve extracted the product description for \"Habbe ziabit 500 mg,\" highlighting its traditional formula and natural composition. Button text has been pulled, like \"\340\246\217\340\246\226\340\246\250\340\246\207 \340\246\205\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\201\340\246\250\" (deep green) and \"\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\266 \340\246\205\340\246\250 \340\246\241\340\247\207\340\246\262\340\246\277\340\246\255\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\" (with a light green badge and truck icon). The right column details, particularly the image of the elderly gentleman, are now under review, and I am now hunting for clues of the hotlinked image.\n\n\n**Locating Source Images**\n\nI\'m now laser-focused on sourcing the necessary images. The user\'s \"hotlink\" suggestion is key; I\'m investigating how to extract them from the provided landing page image. I\'ve begun by searching the workspace to see if there are images already available. If not, I will explore options like cropping, image generation, or directory listings to make sure I have an image or illustration to make the page.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will perform a Skill Check and read the relevant skill instructions for image generation. Then, I will inspect the workspace files and structure to understand the environment and see what assets are available."
