  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Locating Image Sources**\n\nI\'ve hit a snag. The initial assumption about image locations in `/assets` is incorrect. My next step is to investigate potential image generation options or consider hotlinking resources, as the prompt suggests. I\'m focusing on identifying accessible image sources to fulfill the visual requirements of the application.\n\n\n**Exploring Image Possibilities**\n\nOkay, so I\'m realizing the prompt allows either generation OR hotlinking of images. My initial file scans didn\'t reveal pre-existing image assets. I\'m now cross-referencing file content and the screenshot, like the D-CURE Plus bottle. I will focus on a \"D-CURE Plus\" search to see if images can be hotlinked, or whether I will consider generation. I\'m focusing on the \"hotlink\" option!\n\n\n**Considering Image Generation**\n\nI\'m now pivoting to image generation. My focus shifted from hotlinking, and now I\'m thinking of how I can use `generate_image`. I need to generate a product image and a hero image. I\'m going to formulate prompts for both of those images. I\'ve confirmed that there are no existing image files. I\'m breaking down the screenshot to help the prompt, to generate images for the header and hero sections.\n\n\n**Formulating Image Requests**\n\nOkay, the focus is now on generating images. I am planning on making two image generations: one for the \"D-CURE Plus\" bottle as a product image, and another of a bearded man, like a traditional doctor, holding the bottle and blue capsules. The second option is a professional healthcare setting image. I need to build a good text prompt for this, drawing inspiration from the Unani context.\n\n\n**Refining Image Prompts**\n\nI\'m now iterating on my image generation prompts. I\'ve broken down the screenshot and realized the level of detail necessary. For the product display, I\'ll generate an image of a \"D-CURE Plus\" bottle with blue capsules on a clean wooden or modern surface, alongside green leaves. Then, for the healthcare practitioner, I need to generate an image of a bearded, skullcap-wearing practitioner holding the bottle and capsules in a bright clinic setting with \"cedra / NATURAL | PURE | TRUSTED\" on a box behind. I\'ll include the \"\340\246\270\340\247\201\340\246\270\340\247\215\340\246\245 \340\246\271\340\246\250 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\247\203\340\246\244\340\246\277\340\246\225 \340\246\211\340\246\252\340\246\276\340\247\237\340\247\207\" text.\n\n\n**Analyzing Textual Elements**\n\nI\'m now shifting gears to the textual content. I am extracting key information from the \"\340\246\250\340\246\277\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\266\340\246\250\340\246\276 \340\246\223 \340\246\270\340\247\207\340\246\254\340\246\250\340\246\254\340\246\277\340\246\247\340\246\277\" (Directions & Dosage) section. \"\340\246\270\340\247\207\340\246\254\340\246\250 \340\246\256\340\246\276\340\246\244\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276: \340\246\232\340\246\277\340\246\225\340\246\277\340\247\216\340\246\270\340\246\225\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\252\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\266 \340\246\205\340\246\250\340\247\201\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\247\237\340\247\200 \340\246\270\340\247\207\340\246\254\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\245\244\" (Dosage: To be taken as advised by a physician.) and \"\340\246\270\340\246\244\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\225\340\246\244\340\246\276: \340\246\206\340\246\262\340\247\213 \340\246\223 \340\246\206\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\246\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\244\340\246\276 \340\246\245\340\247\207\340\246\225\340\247\207 \340\246\246\340\247\202\340\246\260\340\247\207, \340\246\240\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276 \340\246\223 \340\246\266\340\247\201\340\246\267\340\247\215\340\246\225 \340\246\270\340\247\215\340\246\245\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\207 \340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\226\340\247\201\340\246\250\340\245\244 \340\246\266\340\246\277\340\246\266\340\247\201\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\250\340\246\276\340\246\227\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\254\340\246\276\340\246\207\340\246\260\340\247\207 \340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\226\340\247\201\340\246\250\340\245\244\" (Caution: Keep away from light and moisture, in a cool and dry place. Keep out of reach of children.) are key. I\'ll need to decide how to handle the video gallery section \"\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\241\340\246\277\340\246\223 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\" as well, and \"\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\241\340\246\277\340\246\223 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277 - \340\246\206\340\246\256\340\246\276\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\271\340\246\225 \340\246\223 \340\246\254\340\246\277\340\246\266\340\247\207\340\246\267\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\256\340\246\244\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\244 \340\246\266\340\247\201\340\246\250\340\247\201\340\246\250\".\n\n\n**Conceptualizing Video Content**\n\nI\'m now diving into the video and review sections. For the \"\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\241\340\246\277\340\246\223 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\" (Video Gallery), I will create clickable elements that open a modal player with simulated Unani health awareness content. This will be represented in two videos: \"Unani\'s role in diabetes control\" and \"Customer experiences with D-CURE Plus\". I\'m thinking of creating beautiful modal players, which would host simulated video content.\n\n\n\n**Crafting Consumer Feedback**\n\nI\'m now creating simulated user reviews to enhance credibility. I\'m focusing on crafting positive feedback such as \"\340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\247\207\340\246\234\340\246\277\340\246\202 \340\246\226\340\247\201\340\246\254 \340\246\255\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\247\213 \340\246\217\340\246\254\340\246\202 \340\247\247\340\247\250\340\247\246\340\246\237\340\246\277 \340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\252\340\246\270\340\247\201\340\246\262 \340\246\245\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\246\276\340\247\237 \340\246\205\340\246\250\340\247\207\340\246\225\340\246\246\340\246\277\340\246\250 \340\246\257\340\246\276\340\247\237\340\245\244 \340\246\253\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\253\340\246\262\340\246\223 \340\246\254\340\247\207\340\246\266 \340\246\270\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\247\213\340\246\267\340\246\234\340\246\250\340\246\225\340\245\244\" from Rohima Begum, and another from Abdul Karim, stating \"\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\252\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\266\340\247\207 \340\246\266\340\247\201\340\246\260\340\247\201 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\207\340\246\233\340\246\277\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\245\244 \340\246\205\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\257 \340\246\223\340\246\267\340\247\201\340\246\247\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\244\340\247\201\340\246\262\340\246\250\340\246\276\340\247\237 \340\246\217\340\246\260 \340\246\225\340\247\213\340\246\250\340\247\213 \340\246\270\340\246\276\340\246\207\340\246\241 \340\246\207\340\246\253\340\247\207\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\237 \340\246\254\340\247\201\340\246\235\340\246\277\340\246\250\340\246\277\340\245\244 \340\246\241\340\247\207\340\246\262\340\246\277\340\246\255\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\340\246\223 \340\246\226\340\247\201\340\246\254 \340\246\246\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\247\201\340\246\244 \340\246\252\340\247\207\340\247\237\340\247\207\340\246\233\340\246\277\340\245\244\" I will now focus on the FAQ section.\n\n\n\n**Structuring FAQ Section**\n\nI\'m now concentrating on the FAQ section. I\'ve formulated several questions and answers, focusing on dosage, pregnancy considerations, and usage instructions. I\'m focusing on ensuring these are presented clearly and concisely. I\'m now developing the structure to incorporate these FAQs effectively.\n\nI\'m now integrating the pricing information, specifically \"\340\247\247\340\246\237\340\246\277 \340\246\254\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\270 (\340\247\247\340\247\250\340\247\246 \340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\252\340\246\270\340\247\201\340\246\262)\" - 1 Box (120 Capsules). I\'m focusing on how to best display this alongside the FAQ.\n\n\n**Finalizing Pricing Details**\n\nI\'m now incorporating and refining pricing and order details. I\'m focusing on the presentation of two pricing options. I will have a \"Regular Price\" for 1 box (120 capsules) at \340\247\2631200 with an image of the capsule bottle. The second will be a \"Best Offer\" of 2 boxes (240 capsules) at \340\247\2632000, saving \340\247\263400, visually highlighted with two bottles and a \"Best Offer\" ribbon. Finally, the checkout form, will display these choices for direct ordering, ensuring clarity for the user.\n\n\n**Designing Order Checkout**\n\nI\'m now focusing on designing the order checkout process. I will create fields for user information: name, mobile number, and full address. Placeholders will guide user input. A delivery area selection offers \"\340\246\242\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\244\340\246\260\340\247\207\" and \"\340\246\242\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\254\340\246\276\340\246\207\340\246\260\340\247\207\" with associated charges. A dynamic summary banner displays the total, including delivery, and the order button will be \"\340\246\205\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\225\340\246\250\340\246\253\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\256 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\201\340\246\250\".\n\n\n\n**Refining Footer Elements**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on the footer\'s details. I have the left side containing \"D-CURE Plus,\" the center with links to \"\340\246\227\340\247\213\340\246\252\340\246\250\340\247\200\340\247\237\340\246\244\340\246\276 \340\246\250\340\247\200\340\246\244\340\246\277,\" \"\340\246\266\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\246\276\340\246\254\340\246\262\340\247\200,\" and \"\340\246\257\340\247\213\340\246\227\340\246\276\340\246\257\340\247\213\340\246\227,\" and the right with the copyright notice: \"\302\251 \340\247\250\340\247\246\340\247\250\340\247\252 \340\246\241\340\246\277-\340\246\225\340\246\277\340\246\211\340\246\260 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\270\340\245\244 \340\246\270\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\254\340\246\270\340\247\215\340\246\254\340\246\244\340\247\215\340\246\254 \340\246\270\340\246\202\340\246\260\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\267\340\246\277\340\246\244\340\245\244 \340\246\217\340\246\237\340\246\277 \340\246\217\340\246\225\340\246\237\340\246\277 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\232\340\247\200\340\246\250 \340\246\207\340\246\211\340\246\250\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\200 \340\246\224\340\246\267\340\246\247\340\245\244\" I\'m refining the layout and spacing. I will focus on the UI flow of the entire application.\n\nI am now focusing on order confirmation. When users select a package, and delivery area, the total must immediately update. I must make sure that when someone clicks \"\340\246\205\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\225\340\246\250\340\246\253\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\256 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\201\340\246\250\", it submits to the backend, be it a database or local storage, and pops up a success modal (\"\340\246\205\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\246\260 \340\246\270\340\246\253\340\246\262 \340\246\271\340\247\237\340\247\207\340\246\233\340\247\207!\") displaying the order summary, order ID, and shipping status (e.g., Processing).\n\n\n**Prioritizing User Intent**\n\nI\'m now laser-focused on user experience. My plan involves streamlining the order confirmation process to align precisely with user expectations, as per the guidelines. I will have the order confirmation, including tracking details, directly. I\'m prioritizing direct order confirmation and avoiding extra UI elements. I\'m focusing on simplicity and clarity.\n\n\n\n**Structuring Application Layout**\n\nI am now focusing on the application\'s overall structure, based on the provided screenshot and prompt requirements. I am now creating the foundational layout with the navbar, hero section, and feature cards. I need to make sure the single-page application structure includes all sections and integrates without extra complexities. I am incorporating each of the required sections, ensuring a clear and intuitive user experience.\n\n\n**Crafting UI Elements**\n\nI\'m now implementing the UI elements. I\'m focusing on incorporating the design specifications provided, including the color palette (`#003520`, `#735c00`, `#fed65b`, and `#f7faf8`), fonts (Inter and IBM Plex Sans), and style details (soft tonal layers and rounded corners). I will ensure the application adheres to the brand\'s visual identity. I\'m focusing on the overall consistency and aesthetics.\n\n\n\n"
