  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Constructing Hero Section**\n\nOkay, I\'m now actively constructing the Hero section, starting with `/src/components/Hero.tsx`. I\'ve analyzed the design and I am going to build a large section, with a botanical background. On the left side I see a content column, with a badge. The badge has a leaf icon and background. This is a good starting point.\n\n\n**Styling Badge Elements**\n\nI\'m now styling the badge beautifully. I\'ve chosen a light-green border with deep green text to convey a sense of natural efficacy. The headline, \"\340\246\241\340\246\276\340\247\237\340\246\276\340\246\254\340\247\207\340\246\237\340\246\277\340\246\270 \340\246\250\340\246\277\340\247\237\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\243\340\247\207 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\247\203\340\246\244\340\246\277\340\246\225 \340\246\270\340\246\256\340\246\276\340\246\247\340\246\276\340\246\250\" (Natural Solution to Control Diabetes), and description, \"D-CURE Plus (Habbe ziabit 500 mg) \340\246\271\340\246\262\340\247\213 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\232\340\247\200\340\246\250 \340\246\207\340\246\211\340\246\250\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\200 \340\246\253\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\256\340\247\201\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\247\237 \340\246\244\340\247\210\340\246\260\340\246\277 \340\246\217\340\246\225\340\246\237\340\246\277 \340\246\225\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\200 \340\246\224\340\246\267\340\246\247 \340\246\257\340\246\276 \340\246\260\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\247\207 \340\246\266\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\225\340\246\260\340\246\276 \340\246\256\340\246\276\340\246\244\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276 \340\246\250\340\246\277\340\247\237\340\246\250\340\247\215\340\246\244\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\243\340\247\207 \340\246\270\340\246\271\340\246\276\340\247\237\340\246\244\340\246\276 \340\246\225\340\246\260\340\247\207\340\245\244 \340\246\270\340\246\256\340\247\215\340\246\252\340\247\202\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\243 \340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\225\340\247\203\340\246\244\340\246\277\340\246\225 \340\246\211\340\246\252\340\246\276\340\246\246\340\246\276\340\246\250\340\247\207 \340\246\244\340\247\210\340\246\260\340\246\277, \340\246\225\340\247\213\340\246\250\340\247\213 \340\246\252\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\266\340\247\215\340\246\254\340\246\252\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\244\340\246\277\340\246\225\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\277\340\247\237\340\246\276 \340\246\250\340\247\207\340\246\207\340\245\244\" are set. I will soon be implementing the \"Order Now\" button and the \"Cash on Delivery\" label with their respective icons to create a user-friendly call to action.\n\n\n**Designing Visual Representation**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the visual representation, and I\'m very excited! I\'ve been brainstorming ideas for a compelling visual element for the hero section. I initially considered a card featuring a practitioner, but with image generation limits, I\'ve pivoted to a high-fidelity CSS and vector illustration. I am leaning toward a combination: an SVG background, layered with organic plants, and a realistic Unani medicine container generated via HTML/CSS, with glassmorphism overlays and golden sparkles. It\'s an elegant, premium look that aligns perfectly.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now create the `/src/components/Hero.tsx` component. It includes a biological/green badge, standard high-definition typography for Bangla text layouts with increased height, and a dual-button call to action. On the right, it features a professionally crafted vector illustration combined with a curated high-quality image of herbal capsules to represent the product with supreme clinical authority. This ensures an organic layout that perfectly translates the screenshot."
