    thinking: "**Creating the Component**\n\nI\'m currently focused on developing the `/src/components/WhyChooseUs.tsx` component. I\'ve nailed down the key information: It will feature a title, \"\340\246\225\340\247\207\340\246\250 D-CURE Plus \340\246\254\340\247\207\340\246\233\340\247\207 \340\246\250\340\246\277\340\246\254\340\247\207\340\246\250?\" (Why choose D-CURE Plus?), and a subtitle highlighting the capsule\'s quality and focus on health. I am proceeding!\n\n\n**Defining the Benefits**\n\nI\'ve determined the detailed content for the component\'s card section. I\'ll include three cards, each focusing on a specific benefit. The first will address sugar control with a green icon, the second a Unani formula with a yellow icon, and the third, yet to be completed, will be a dark green icon. I have the titles and content locked down, and now I just need the icons.\n\n\n"
