  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Constructing the Interactive Section**\n\nOkay, I\'m digging into `/src/components/VideoGallery.tsx` now. Based on the screenshot, it\'s pretty clear: I\'ve got a title, \"\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\241\340\246\277\340\246\223 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\257\340\246\276\340\246\262\340\246\276\340\246\260\340\246\277\" and a subtitle, \"\340\246\206\340\246\256\340\246\276\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\271\340\246\225 \340\246\223 \340\246\254\340\246\277\340\246\266\340\247\207\340\246\267\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\246\246\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\256\340\246\244\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\244 \340\246\266\340\247\201\340\246\250\340\247\201\340\246\250\". This is the foundation; now, let\'s explore the structure to make it interactive.\n\n\n**Analyzing the Video Section**\n\nI\'m now outlining the video grid\'s structure. Two cards will feature background images with play buttons, and bottom text blocks for headers and subtitles. Card 1 focuses on expert advice (\"\340\246\254\340\246\277\340\246\266\340\247\207\340\246\267\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\252\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\266\") about diabetes management in Unani medicine, and card 2 highlights customer experiences (\"\340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\271\340\246\225\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\205\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\246\244\340\246\276\") with D-CURE Plus. I\'m aiming for a visually engaging design to enhance the user experience.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I will now create `/src/components/VideoGallery.tsx`. This section includes two video preview cards (\"\340\246\254\340\246\277\340\246\266\340\247\207\340\246\267\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\252\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\256\340\246\260\340\247\215\340\246\266\", \"\340\246\227\340\247\215\340\246\260\340\246\276\340\246\271\340\246\225\340\247\207\340\246\260 \340\246\205\340\246\255\340\246\277\340\246\234\340\247\215\340\246\236\340\246\244\340\246\276\"), detailed with a circular play button overlay. When clicked, it launches an elegant **Interactive Video Modal**, embedding a custom-engineered, fully controlled HTML video player (simulating a clinical testimonial broadcast with captions, pause states, and scrub animation). This delivers a premium media experience."
    thinking_duration {
