    modified_response: "I will now create the `/src/components/CheckoutForm.tsx` booking controller. It takes the package selected state as props, features steps for package and delivery routing, validates form details securely, and updates prices instantly in real-time according to delivery zone selections (\340\247\263\340\247\254\340\247\246 inside Dhaka vs \340\247\263\340\247\247\340\247\250\340\247\246 outside). It triggers the invoice modal upon completion."
