  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Reviewing Our Progress**\n\nI\'m pleased to report a flawless build! Now, I\'m shifting focus to reviewing the implementation. Specifically, I\'ve implemented essential structures within `/src/types.ts`, covering options, reviews, FAQs, order payloads, and live tracking. The next step is a deep dive into the data model found in `/src/data.ts`.\n\n\n**Analyzing Component Functionality**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on the detailed functionality of key components. Specifically, I\'m analyzing the Bengali translation texts and how they will be integrated, alongside package definitions, including savings indicators and popular tags. I\'m also examining the verified reviews and the structure of the FAQ accordion pairs. I\'m then examining the `/src/components/Navbar.tsx`, `/src/components/Hero.tsx`, `/src/components/WhyChooseUs.tsx`, `/src/components/DosageGuide.tsx`, and `/src/components/VideoGallery.tsx` components.\n\n\n**Evaluating User Experience**\n\nI am now thoroughly evaluating the user experience, particularly concerning component interactions and data display. Specifically, I\'m examining the `CustomerReviews` component, noting the five-star rating grids, and styling. The `BannerMiddle` component, which displays the quality seal grid is also being examined, especially its green GMP certified display. Finally, I\'m considering the FAQ accordion, pricing panels, the checkout form with secure input validation, and the order success modal with the four-step tracker.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have designed and built a highly polished, interactive single-page landing application for **D-CURE Plus** (Habbe ziabit 500 mg). It matches the precise visual layout, typographic scale, and slate-organic tones shown in your screenshot.\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Typographic Pairing\n*   **Medical Corporate Aesthetic**: Developed a clean, trust-inspiring canvas utilizing soft greens, gold accents, and clinical off-white tonal layups (`#F7FAF8`) to emphasize ancient Unani heritage alongside modern medicine precision.\n*   **Bangla Typography Optimization**: Integrated **IBM Plex Sans Bangla** for display headings to convey an authoritative, systematic layout, paired with **Inter** for readable body copy. Increased the line-height vertical spacing by 20% to optimize Bangla script readability.\n\n### \342\232\241 Interactive Features & User Experience\n*   **Dynamic Dosage Tracker**: Implemented a specialized, locally-powered tracker widget. Customers can mark daily doses (Morning & Night) to advance a radial completion ring. Completing the daily quota displays a success badge with a leaf icon in \"Natural Green.\"\n*   **Interactive Video Testimonials Modal**: Clicking on any expert or customer video preview launches an elegant custom video popup with playback controls, subtitle simulations, and interactive captions.\n*   **Cohesive Package Booking**: Navigating through the pricing table allows users to select a package, which instantly updates the selected tier in the checkout form below and scrolls to the checkout section.\n*   **Real-time Invoice & Order Tracking**: The checkout controller includes real-time price updates (handling local delivery zone calculations of \340\247\263\340\247\254\340\247\246 for inside Dhaka vs \340\247\263\340\247\247\340\247\250\340\247\246 for outside). On submission, it validates form inputs and opens an **Order Receipt Invoice** complete with an animated **Four-Step Order Tracking Progress Bar** (Received \342\236\224 Packing \342\236\224 Shipped \342\236\224 Delivered).\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 680800925
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
